b"FUTURECRAFT.STRUNG\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
Imagine a shoe that's so synced to you, you almost can't feel it. STRUNG is first-of-its-kind textile creation tech made for just that. Our first proof of concept is\xc2\xa0FUTURECRAFT.STRUNG, made in partnership with @kram_weisshaar.

Read more now at adidas.com/futurecraft/strung #FUTURECRAFT"

b'Pride is about coming together in joy, unity and solidarity - and now more than ever that spirit is needed. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3 \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
At the heart of the modern LGBTQ+ rights movement is the work of Black transgender and gender non-conforming activists during the Stonewall Riots. Today their fight continues not just for equal representation and rights, but for their lives. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3 \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
We understand that change happens when we work together and amplify each other, so with @AthleteAlly and @StonewallUK, we are celebrating\xc2\xa0the people\xc2\xa0from across our community. Swipe through to read their thoughts on what Pride represents for them and what it means to be an ally. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3 \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3

b'This is our commitment to the Black community, and the world. We can change, and we will. This is just the start.'
b'Take action. Things won\xe2\x80\x99t change unless we create that change.'
